      • createNonterminal

        public Nonterminal createNonterminal(String label,
                                     int rank,
                                     boolean[] isReductionTentacle)
        Creates a Nonterminal symbol with the provided parameters.
        Parameters:
        label - The label of the Nonterminal symbol.
        rank - The number of nodes that have to be attached to an edge labeled with this Nonterminal.
        isReductionTentacle - An array of length rank that determines for each tentacle whether it is a reduction tentacle or not. The i-th tentacle is a reduction tentacle if replacing a hyperedge labeled with this Nonterminal never creates an outgoing edge at the i-th external node.
        Returns:
        The Nonterminal.
